{"tid":1405414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[訴求升級] 解散警隊！解散警隊！","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:04.000Z","uid":135623,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d036514b6da35ca2a027d084a172ef1e351a61d0","tid":1405414,"uid":135623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"而家個政府根本腐敗到不得了，官官相衛，分分鐘查三五七年之後捉幾個替死鬼就算<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有狗隻即時停職接受調查，重組警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"426bfbe42bb0bc2211da2571ca1ec01b404071be","tid":1405414,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n絕對係路軌練跑<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span></span>"},{"pid":"88d69686bdca01a8388d51df0679151c4ec79801","tid":1405414,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693155ac9119c88d2159498e0e63331b3089bd94","tid":1405414,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a964a02c6a2474cd